					<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/articles-by-jack/why-wont-libertarians-admit-what-government-has-done-right/comment-page-1?replytocom=194461#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-194461", "194461", "respond", "3330")'>Reply</a>								</span><!-- .comment-meta .commentmetadata -->
