		<div class="comment-body"><p>I had someone argue to me that all Americans are socialist, to a greater or lesser degree, because we utilize &#8220;free&#8221; government services.</p>
<p>Trust me, nothing is &#8220;free&#8221; to me, I couldn&#8217;t possibly receive enough government services to account for the taxes I&#8217;ve had extorted from me.</p>
