		<div class="comment-body"><p>First I Think the car analogy is perfect for the current healthcare debate.<br />
Second, read the Declaration of Independence.  Pretty simple concepts.<br />
Do not assault or infringe upon anyones natural born rights and everyone can get along.  people are way to far into what other people do.  As long as it does not affect you or anothers natural born rights get over it.  I dont remember one of our basic rights to be telling others how to live there own lives.  Government at any level only role is a referee for the natural born rights of the population it is refereeing, while we the people closely watch and referee the referees.  Lastly we have no use for republicans, democrats, libertarians, and what have you. just created to further divide the populous.<br />
Freedom is simple.</p>
